CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 12, 1941, pg. 17, reads: "Cuban Stars All Set For Clash With Grays - Here are the colorful Cuban Stars who will clash with the Homestead Grays here Sunday at Forbes Field in feature attraction of a gigantic Elks' Day celebration. The doubleheader was originally scheduled for July 4, but postponed because of rain. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of the New York Cubans baseball team lined up in dugout at Forbes Field for Elks' Day celebration
